nodes.text: A RA-7 protocol droid was on Coruscant with an astromech droid in 21 BBY during the Clone Wars. The RA-7 protocol droid and astromech droid were both in a dark alley in the lower market districts of Coruscant. When assassin droid HELIOS-3E and techno-service droid Todo 360 were pursuing R2 series astromech droid R2-D2, HELIOS-3D, thinking it had discovered R2, stunned the RA-7's astromech droid companion. The RA-7 was startled and ran away, believing that the astromech had been killed
